{"tid":950404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［黑店］睇鐵打比醫師非禮","createTime":"2018-12-21T13:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T14:22:28.000Z","uid":216387,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ec5ea99dba495eb3abecc08742a749e8752fe16f","tid":950404,"uid":216387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:25:13.000Z","msg":"前日我拗柴行唔到，朋友推張輪椅送我去<strong>鐘發鐵打舖</strong>睇鐵打，然後醫師熊抱我個胸上床 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n示意圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zVX9H66.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzVX9H66.png&h=43a0c029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n期間佢想試下我隻腳嘅承受力叫我訓係張床上面趌高patpat，我未明佢想我做咩佢就開始摸同托我patpat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最尾我離開嗰陣佢仲想衝出黎抱我上輪椅，好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好後悔嗰陣冇即刻話佢，仲幫佢諗藉口，而家覺得成件事好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女仔去睇鐵打真係要小心，我有朋友陪同都係咁，真係要好好保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後唔會再去呢間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>黑店 鐘發跌打舖</strong><br />\n地址：德民街29號黃埔新邨德民大廈<br />\n電話：2334 9191"},{"pid":"d21fbf7235b7f59cbe49195387a398dbfa414ca7","tid":950404,"uid":10844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:29:03.000Z","msg":"Me too<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d373923d61728f4b168b4036821674709b675bc","tid":950404,"uid":28277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:33:10.000Z","msg":"佢好似唔正常做法"},{"pid":"b0c21e7bd310627cd16ddb10ad006949ccc46fdf","tid":950404,"uid":1082,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:36:44.000Z","msg":"當場又唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事後post 上黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n報警呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a41b2bbe1b2ee199432e6cefe25301416328f23","tid":950404,"uid":154106,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:37:23.000Z","msg":"男人老狗又唔係撩你碌鳩"},{"pid":"b7fe6cf2252797dc6c00d100d508a420f0ca62a8","tid":950404,"uid":37226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:38:22.000Z","msg":"個廢老老到邊度有問題都唔記得<br />\n講完隻手轉個身去左按腳問邊度痛<br />\n唔明點解仲有咁多人去睇"},{"pid":"e9fbd1f7cf7b43804aa8a670f92aeb9ed662c280","tid":950404,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:39:18.000Z","msg":"你男人老狗怕西<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c611b3b1957814af46a1c65894353911c4e4cf","tid":950404,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:39:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db97d8a1377dea8ccc975f5e77b9d6caab5ddaa0","tid":950404,"uid":216387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e9fbd1f7cf7b43804aa8a670f92aeb9ed662c280","tid":950404,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:39:18.000Z","msg":"你男人老狗怕西<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:42:38.000Z","msg":"我係女.."},{"pid":